4. ROW_NUMBER()
syntax : ROWS BETWEEN <start> AND <end>

Most Important Interview Patterns
> Running Total
SUM() OVER (
    ORDER BY col
    ROWS BETWEEN UNBOUNDED PRECEDING
    AND CURRENT ROW
)
